Phase 5 - Deployment and Release
--------------------------------

Security Activities
• Infrastructure security validation
• Configuration review
• Security baseline verification
• Change management approval
• Pre-production security checks

Tools & Technologies
• IaC scanning: Checkov, Terrascan, tfsec
• Container security: Prisma Cloud, Aqua Security
• Configuration management: Ansible, Chef, Puppet
• CI/CD security: Jenkins with security plugins, GitLab CI
• Cloud security: AWS Security Hub, Azure Security Center

Methodologies & Standards
• Infrastructure as Code security
• Immutable infrastructure
• Blue-green deployment
• Canary releases with monitoring
• Security hardening baselines (CIS benchmarks)

Key Deliverables
• Deployment security checklist completed
• Infrastructure scan results
• Security configuration validation
• Change approval with security sign-off
• Rollback plan
